<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，再见！” 尼娜抱了抱妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天她们一起走到儿童中心夏令营。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，宝贝儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我和秀晶阿姨三点来接你。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 今天，韩国的秀晶阿姨会来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会在尼娜家里住一个星期。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望今天做手工。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样我就可以送给秀晶阿姨。” 尼娜想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>体育馆里，邓恩老师拿着一箱草莓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪在猜里面有多少个草莓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十二。” 莉琪说，“我猜有二十二个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得呢，尼娜？” 邓恩老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天要做食物吗？” 她失望地问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不做手工吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做冰沙！” 贾森猜道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不对。但是你们也会喜欢的。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做草莓酱。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们做过草莓酱吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没做过。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我妈妈做过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快，你就可以帮她了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很简单的。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们要把这些草莓洗一洗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦，你可以帮忙洗吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你还可以数一数到底有几个。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“三十二个！” 伊坦告诉他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，你猜错了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“切、切、切。” 尼娜切掉草莓的顶部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“无聊、无聊、无聊。” 她不开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>切好以后，邓恩老师把草莓分到五个碗里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起一些捣碎器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个人拿一个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！” 伊坦欢呼道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要把东西捣碎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈，太好玩儿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪用捣碎器捣碎草莓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也很脏。” 尼娜指了指莉琪的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面全是草莓汁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。可以开始煮了。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“煮？要煮草莓吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。加热可以让糖融化。” 邓恩老师解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在把碗里的草莓倒进锅里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后加入一杯半白糖。” 波比念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“加两汤匙柠檬汁。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用小火加热到糖融化。” 贾森念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么知道糖融化了没有呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在糖是白色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当它融化时，我们就看不到它了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它会变成透明的糖浆！” 邓恩老师解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着锅里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它在融化！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在把火开大，煮沸！” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了搅拌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森把一个木头勺子给尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“颜色真好看。” 尼娜边搅拌边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在可以把酱倒进罐子里了。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，我们把它放凉，再放入冰箱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，邓恩老师从冰箱里拿出罐子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有一些蝴蝶结和卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以装饰罐子，然后送给别人。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“送给别人？” 尼娜想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 活动结束了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜跑出来跟妈妈和秀晶阿姨打招呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“秀晶阿姨！” 她大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个酱是送给您的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，尼娜。” 秀晶阿姨抱着她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：“甜甜的东西给甜甜的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>